author: Reuters Editorial
title: FBC Says FY Group Profit Before Income Tax Increased By 14 Pct
text:
March 29 (Reuters) - FBC Holdings Ltd:
* FY GROUP PROFIT BEFORE INCOME TAX INCREASED BY 14% TO US$29.3 MILLION‍​
* FY NET ASSET VALUE 21.53 US CENTS PER SHARE * FY TOTAL INCOME FOR THE GROUP WAS UP 13% TO US$105.3 MILLION
* “TO CONTINUE PURSUING INITIATIVES THAT WILL RESULT IN THE FURTHER REDUCTION OF OUR COST OF FUNDS”
* NET INCOME FROM PROPERTY SALES WAS UP 22% TO US$1.2 MILLION IN 2017
* 2017 FINAL DIVIDEND OF 0.8417 US CENTS PER SHARE WAS PROPOSED Source text ID: ( bit.ly/2usLPw3 ) Further company coverage:
